{"type": "article", "id": 15464, "title": "球形天蓬", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-24T06:34:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 124, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016070213555545XwN6MZ7J0otQTO.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这个透明的球形天蓬，正好放在花园里遮风挡雨，相当于圈起了一个温室。坐在里面就像坐在了自然中，是个看书、睡觉、喝茶的好地方。球形结构自带保护感，它还能反射阳光促进周围植物的光合作用。完全采用可回收材料，直径 3.6 米，高 2.2 米，还可另购一块米色布的配件，<a href=\"http://gardenigloo.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142546G08HP7CgopuTIEVX.jpg\" width=\"721\" height=\"479\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66435506\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261425468Wbt9fFvSqz5JxBR.jpg\" width=\"721\" height=\"479\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66435506\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142547zv53rEUqbN9M2iD8.jpg\" width=\"721\" height=\"479\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66435506\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142547F0PJyLrD8x47l6ds.jpg\" width=\"721\" height=\"406\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5631068\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}